high_descs: Turn left at the cardboard box and take a left at the wall to reach the small nightstand next to the bed.
Pick up the cell phone from the back left corner of the nightstand.
Turn around, hang a right at the end of the bed and walk to the table on the left.
Put the cell phone to the right of the laptop computer on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cell phone on a table.

high_descs: Turn left walk toward the wall then turn left facing the side table
Pick up the phone on the side table
Turn left then head to the desk
Put the phone on the desk in front of the laptop
anns.task_desc: Put the phone on the desk

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the night stand.
Pick up the phone that's in front of you on the night stand to the left of the alarm clock.
Turn around and walk to the desk with the laptop on it.
Put the phone on the desk under the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone on the desk.
